information: bertelli formaggi s.r.l. has been on the market for four generations trading excellent quality fresh and aged cheeses. we are a reference point for many european businesses when it comes to supplying not only parmigiano reggiano that has been aged from 12 to 60 months but also traditional italian goat and sheep cheese. we also supply typical charcuterie such as salami, fiocchetto, mortadella, parma ham, bresaola and may others.

products_and_services: cheese | sicilian cheese supplier | italian cheese supplier | sicilian wine supplier | sicilian food supplier
information: nuova commerciale siciliana s.r.l. refines, trades and distributes food and wine since 1979. in the last 35 years the company has developed a complete range of services, customised according to the needs of the hospitality, horeca and food and wine sectors. it refers to the owners and managers of restaurants, deli and typical products shops, pub, hotel, farm holidays, cruises, supermarkets and similar, export companies and other dealers. it offers to the food and wine sector a selected assortment of typical sicilian products, with a particular attention towards the sicilian typical cheeses, as the sicilian pecorino (sheep) cheese, the piacentinu ennese (cheese with saffron), the tuma persa, the cosacavaddu ibleo, the nebrodian provola cheese, the maiorchino and the vastedda del belice. in 2001, the company becomes the solely distributor of the formidoro branded dairy products, representing the excellence of ricotta, sheep and goat cheeses, handmade by using milk coming from sicilian livestock only, and according to the ancient regional traditions. the company offers moreover dairy products coming from other italian regions, a wide range of cold cuts, preserved, pasta sauces and seasoning, frozen foods, wine, liqueurs, spirits and other specific products for the hospitality sector.

information: nord sardegna lane s.r.l.s. (nsw) is the largest exporter of sardinian sheep wool in european and foreign markets, with a capacity of more than 1.5 million kilos (+3.000.000 lbs) per year. our company can provide also high quantities of sardinian lamb skins, well known with name of "toscana", in wet salted and air-dried condition, suitable for shearling, suede and all double-face production of very light weight fur garments, coats and collars. we can supply sheep skins, goat/kid skins and cattle hides as well. our headquarters are in 3 strategic points across the island bonnanaro (sassari-ss) macomer (nuoro-nu) marrubiu (oristano-or) in way to cover the whole territory to fulfill any kind of quality requirement.
